OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny isolated
OL,6,Fdaytime showers fading with most
OL,7,Fseeing clear spells overnight with
OL,8,Fintermittent areas of cloud. Winds
OL,9,Fdropping out and staying mild
OL,10,Fovernight, but more comfortable than
OL,11,Frecent nights.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA fine start to the weekend
OL,14,Fwith prolonged periods of sunshine.
OL,15,FCloud building a little more in the
OL,16,Fafternoon with an isolated shower
OL,17,Fpossible, but many staying dry. Less
OL,18,Fhot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
