OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStaying
OL,6,Fdry into the second half of the
OL,7,Fweekend and next week, with sunny
OL,8,Fspells by day and clear skies at
OL,9,Fnight. Temperatures dropping a little,
OL,10,Fbut still feeling warm.
